l instead of Wordpress?</blockquote><br />\n有用過<br />\n<br />\n但太慢近來轉咗用hugo"},{"pid":"de572e6ecdef09edd9474e58e1145a9e3b04fd6b","tid":390521,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T07:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Anybody is using Jekyll instead of Wordpress?</blockquote><br />\n有用過<br />\n<br />\n但太慢近來轉咗用hugo</blockquote><br />\nstatic都慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有新野 hugo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngoogle下先"},{"pid":"6aff4205a08722c7e8345d0209dac74ccb174cf8","tid":390521,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Anybody is using Jekyll instead of Wordpress?</blockquote><br />\n有用過<br />\n<br />\n但太慢近來轉咗用hugo</blockquote><br />\nstatic都慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有新野 hugo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngoogle下先</blockquote><br />\n當你有咁上下文既時候Jekyll Compile同Reindexing都幾慢下<br />\n本身係Ruby底無法"},{"pid":"68a42d12e694c6999da562783398c2ee8d35e6ff","tid":390521,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T21:53:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66afd7f5e01b331b21ae38f0e9e60b18cb8e6ae4","tid":390521,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話時話最近開左個wordpress,諗住用黎放photos同打blog用<br />\n<br />\n但係爬左好耐文都搵唔到有咩方法可以係唔同頁面分別顯示兩種posts<br />\n(photos同blog)<br />\n<br />\n見到有人話用category,姐係開一個photos既category,再開一個blog既category,然後係menu到放哂2種category<br />\n<br />\n但係咁樣做之後其實兩種post都係共同,姐係我會係phtots果頁見到blog既tag同recent posts咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇方法可以完全分開2個頁面去睇posts? <br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCustom post type + taxonomy <br />\n之後有需要就自己寫個 Template 任你 loop 到天花龍鳳都得<br />\n<br />\n利申最撚憎用WordPress"},{"pid":"4ad6a2054a8274703c8c7f3aeaa53001d46ef505","tid":390521,"uid":73422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:03:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f79e188735a394d3695067c5b30a222d0baf2670","tid":390521,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Anybody is using Jekyll instead of Wordpress?</blockquote><br />\n有用過<br />\n<br />\n但太慢近來轉咗用hugo</blockquote><br />\nstatic都慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有新野 hugo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngoogle下先</blockquote><br />\n當你有咁上下文既時候Jekyll Compile同Reindexing都幾慢下<br />\n本身係Ruby底無法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學左陣Jeykll<br />\n一D 都唔覺得好用<br />\nD Markdown extend 完又extend<br />\n下下都要自己build野<br />\n<br />\n用番wordpress算，比人水左"},{"pid":"d6d34d6adf7992bfb5866642fc39df0b7af9bcd0","tid":390521,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Anybody is using Jekyll instead of Wordpress?</blockquote><br />\n有用過<br />\n<br />\n但太慢近來轉咗用hugo</blockquote><br />\nstatic都慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有新野 hugo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngoogle下先</blockquote><br />\n當你有咁上下文既時候Jekyll Compile同Reindexing都幾慢下<br />\n本身係Ruby底無法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學左陣Jeykll<br />\n一D 都唔覺得好用<br />\nD Markdown extend 完又extend<br />\n下下都要自己build野<br />\n<br />\n用番wordpress算，比人水左</blockquote><br />\n而且係似寫緊Ruby(利申:未用過Ruby):<br />\n<br />\n{% if page.url == '/' %}current{% endif %}"},{"pid":"942829f0d0abcd9a54e49b15d053597cc12a3d1c","tid":390521,"uid":85524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Anybody is using Jekyll instead of Wordpress?</blockquote><br />\n有用過<br />\n<br />\n但太慢近來轉咗用hugo</blockquote><br />\nstatic都慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有新野 hugo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngoogle下先</blockquote><br />\n當你有咁上下文既時候Jekyll Compile同Reindexing都幾慢下<br />\n本身係Ruby底無法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學左陣Jeykll<br />\n一D 都唔覺得好用<br />\nD Markdown extend 完又extend<br />\n下下都要自己build野<br />\n<br />\n用番wordpress算，比人水左</blockquote><br />\n而且係似寫緊Django<br />\n<br />\n{% if page.url == '/' %}current{% endif %}</blockquote>"}]}